Ken Auletta , author and New Yorker 
writer, says the public has yet to find out the extent of 
government surveillance on them. Auletta talks with Bloomberg's 
Tom Keene, Scarlet Fu and Alix Steele on Bloomberg Radio's 
"Bloomberg Surveillance."  (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 01:38
 